#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.151"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.151:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.151:0.2"
msgid "15. Ariyavagga "
msgstr "15. The Noble Path "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.151:0.3"
msgid "151. Bhāvetabbasutta "
msgstr "151. Should Be Developed "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.151:1.1"
msgid "“Bhāvetabbañca vo, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ desessāmi na bhāvetabbañca. "
msgstr "“I will teach you the principle to develop and the principle not to develop. … "

msgctxt "an10.151:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.151:1.3"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, na bhāvetabbo dhammo? "
msgstr "And what is the principle not to develop? "

msgctxt "an10.151:1.4"
msgid "Micchādiṭṭhi … pe … micchāvimutti—"
msgstr "Wrong view, wrong thought, wrong speech, wrong action, wrong livelihood, wrong effort, wrong mindfulness, wrong immersion, wrong knowledge, and wrong freedom. "

msgctxt "an10.151:1.5"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, na bhāvetabbo dhammo. "
msgstr "This is called the principle not to develop. "

msgctxt "an10.151:1.6"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, bhāvetabbo dhammo? "
msgstr "And what is the principle to develop? "

msgctxt "an10.151:1.7"
msgid "Sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāvimutti—"
msgstr "Right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, right immersion, right knowledge, and right freedom. "

msgctxt "an10.151:1.8"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, bhāvetabbo dhammo”ti. "
msgstr "This is called the principle to develop.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.151:1.9"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
